{"tid":1552524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"家母好叻女，識得分辨鬼","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T11:10:30.000Z","uid":252199,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"298f62d6a2c42de7a4fed8aa16c277c0e05a01a7","tid":1552524,"uid":252199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"剛才我地一家喺九龍站上車<br />\n已經見到好多手足<br />\n<br />\n(Sor9ly  冇罷到黨鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n點知我老母好眼厲<br />\n一嘢見到一位著黑色背心<br />\n但雙臂雪白 （咁又未至於白到似女人嘅）<br />\n戴藍色口罩<br />\n剃軍裝頭嘅男人<br />\n就話呢啲一定係鬼<br />\n（佢同行都仲有兩個人）<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;啲細路發夢發左咁多個月<br />\n梗係黑姑甩掘啦<br />\n點會成隻白皮豬咁&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你睇下呢啲細路<br />\n黑咪媽咁架嘛<br />\n啲神情都咁純真<br />\n唔似果個人囉<br />\n呢啲一定喺學堂仲訓練緊，或者啱啱出黎果啲&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我地落左車再留意下<br />\n點知佢地一行三人去到中環站就分開行<br />\n一個去柴灣方向月台上車<br />\n一個走向 ABCD 出口嘅電梯<br />\n至於果個男人就走向JK出口果邊方向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9208961ec1123723e0e40c4eb3f8c71cdea2da4c","tid":1552524,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"勇武照計都係包實, 唔會曬黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6701e1c7b931534d075ae1f43d128f08922ce8d1","tid":1552524,"uid":120431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9208961ec1123723e0e40c4eb3f8c71cdea2da4c","tid":1552524,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"勇武照計都係包實, 唔會曬黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804f3bf36a1b399ee4ff741c5462acbadf1b572b","tid":1552524,"uid":252199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9208961e